snippet.title: Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet Complete Edition Launch Trailer | PS4, X1, PC
snippet.description:
Live the full story of Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet when the Complete Edition launches with ALL DLC chapters! Jump in to the story with your ArFa-sys and become the ultimate hero, as you traverse through the world of Gun Gale Online.  Plus, explore the expansion pack Dissonance of the Nexus, giving you the full scope of what it means to be a hero! 

Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet Complete Edition launches on PS4, XB1, and PC on January 19th, 2019.  Additionally, Sword Art Online Hollow Realization will release on the Nintendo Switch in the summer of 2019 and Sword Art Online Fatal Bullet: Complete Edition will release on Nintendo Switch at a later date: https://bandainam.co/SAOFB
